### Auth - confirm OTP
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/confirm-otp
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "abc@gmail.com",
  "otp": "Iamabc@123"
}

### Auth - login
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "abc@gmail.com",
  "password": "Iamabc@123"
}

### Auth - request password-reset OTP
