Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "iamfake942@gmail.com"
}

### Auth - verify password-reset OTP
# Save resetToken from this response only in frontend memory.
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/verify-forgot-password-otp
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "iamfake942@gmail.com",
  "otp": "201523"
}

