### Auth - Google login
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/google
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "credential": "<GOOGLE_ID_TOKEN>"
}

### Auth - refresh token
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/refresh

### Auth - logout
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/logout

### Auth - current user
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Products - list available products
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/products?page=1&limit=12

### Products - list available products price low to high
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/products?page=1&limit=12&price=low-to-high

### Products - list available products price high to low
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/products?page=1&limit=12&price=high-to-low

### Products - list by brand
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/products/brand/samsung

### Products - product details
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/products/vivo-x300-fe-5g-512-gb-12-gb-ram-noir-black-mobile-phone-mowuvm-10060595

### Products - search
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/products/search/query?q=iphone

### Brands - list brands
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/brands

### Brands - products by brand
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/brands/<brand-slug>/products

### Cart - get cart
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/cart
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Cart - add item
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/cart/items/19fd08a4-4ee8-4e14-8d20-cc6b08ff
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "product_id": "<product-id>",
  "quantity": 1
}

### Cart - update item quantity
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/cart/items/<product-id>
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "quantity": 2
}

### Cart - remove item
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/cart/items/<product-id>
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Cart - clear cart
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/cart
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

