### Profile - create address
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/profile/addresses
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "label": "Home",
  "address_line1": "123 Main Street",
  "address_line2": "Apt 4B",
  "city": "Surat",
  "state": "Gujarat",
  "postal_code": "400001",
  "country": "India",
  "latitude": 19.0760,
  "longitude": 72.8777,
  "is_default": false
}

### Profile - update address
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/profile/addresses/<address-id>
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "label": "Office",
  "address_line1": "456 Business Park",
  "city": "Pune",
  "state": "Maharashtra",
  "postal_code": "411001",
  "country": "India",
  "latitude": 18.5204,
  "longitude": 73.8567,
  "is_default": false
}

### Profile - delete address
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/profile/addresses/<address-id>
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Profile - set default address
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/profile/addresses/<address-id>/default
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
